n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/6-cong-nghe-am-thanh-hang-dau-thay-doi-cach-chung-ta-nghe-va-cam-nhan\/#cong_nghe_am_thanh_3d\" >C\u00f4ng Ngh\u1ec7 \u00c2m Thanh 3D<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/6-cong-nghe-am-thanh-hang-dau-thay-doi-cach-chung-ta-nghe-va-cam-nhan\/#cong_nghe_high-resolution_audio\" >C\u00f4ng Ngh\u1ec7 High-Resolution Audio<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/6-cong-nghe-am-thanh-hang-dau-thay-doi-cach-chung-ta-nghe-va-cam-nhan\/#cong_nghe_am_thanh_lossless_compression\" >C\u00f4ng Ngh\u1ec7 \u00c2m Thanh Lossless Compression<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/6-cong-nghe-am-thanh-hang-dau-thay-doi-cach-chung-ta-nghe-va-cam-nhan\/#cong_nghe_am_thanh_immersive\" >C\u00f4ng Ngh\u1ec7 \u00c2m Thanh Immersive<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/6-cong-nghe-am-thanh-hang-dau-thay-doi-cach-chung-ta-nghe-va-cam-nhan\/#cong_nghe_am_thanh_dieu_chinh_theo_moi_truong\" >C\u00f4ng Ngh\u1ec7 \u00c2m Thanh \u0110i\u1ec1u Ch\u1ec9nh Theo M\u00f4i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/6-cong-nghe-am-thanh-hang-dau-thay-doi-cach-chung-ta-nghe-va-cam-nhan\/#cong_nghe_am_thanh_ket_noi_khong_day\" >C\u00f4ng Ngh\u1ec7 \u00c2m Thanh K\u1ebft N\u1ed1i Kh\u00f4ng D\u00e2y<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>Trong th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u00e2m thanh hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m nghe nh\u00ecn t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u00e1u c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u00e2m thanh h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang ta t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c v\u00e0 \u00e2m thanh xung quanh.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16083\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-1.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-1.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-1-600x400.webp 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-1-768x512.webp 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong_nghe_am_thanh_3d\"><\/span>C\u00f4ng Ngh\u1ec7 \u00c2m Thanh 3D<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>\u00c2m thanh 3D, hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u00e2m thanh v\u00f2m, t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian \u00e2m thanh ba chi\u1ec1u, cho ph\u00e9p ng\u01b0\u1eddi nghe c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u00e2m thanh t\u1eeb m\u1ecdi h\u01b0\u1edbng. C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c thu\u1eadt to\u00e1n ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch v\u00e0 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o \u00e2m thanh, mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ch\u00e2n th\u1ef1c nh\u01b0 \u0111ang \u1edf trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea1c hay r\u1ea1p chi\u1ebfu phim.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16081\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-5.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"599\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-5.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-5-601x400.webp 601w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-5-768x511.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-5-600x399.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong_nghe_high-resolution_audio\"><\/span>C\u00f4ng Ngh\u1ec7 High-Resolution Audio<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>High-Resolution Audio (Hi-Res Audio) l\u00e0 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n \u00e2m thanh v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i cao h\u01a1n CD ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n, cung c\u1ea5p ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e2m thanh chi ti\u1ebft v\u00e0 s\u1eafc n\u00e9t h\u01a1n. Hi-Res Audio gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin \u00e2m thanh h\u01a1n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ghi \u00e2m, mang l\u1ea1i tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m nghe g\u1ea7n g\u0169i v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n g\u1ed1c.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16082\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-6.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-6.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-6-600x400.webp 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-6-768x512.webp 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong_nghe_am_thanh_lossless_compression\"><\/span>C\u00f4ng Ngh\u1ec7 \u00c2m Thanh Lossless Compression<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>N\u00e9n \u00e2m thanh kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t (Lossless Compression) cho ph\u00e9p gi\u1ea3m dung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng file \u00e2m thanh m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap vi\u1ec7c l\u01b0u tr\u1eef v\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i d\u1eef li\u1ec7u \u00e2m thanh tr\u1edf n\u00ean hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m nghe.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16080\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-4.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-4.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-4-600x400.webp 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-4-768x512.webp 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong_nghe_am_thanh_immersive\"><\/span>C\u00f4ng Ngh\u1ec7 \u00c2m Thanh Immersive<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>\u00c2m thanh Immersive, hay \u00e2m thanh \u0111\u1eafm ch\u00ecm, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn m\u1edbi trong c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u00e2m thanh, t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m nghe \u0111a chi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 \u0111a c\u1ea3m x\u00fac. C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong c\u00e1c tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i video v\u00e0 phim \u1ea3nh, n\u01a1i m\u00e0 \u00e2m thanh \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1ea3o s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16079\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-3.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-3.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-3-600x400.webp 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-3-768x512.webp 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong_nghe_am_thanh_dieu_chinh_theo_moi_truong\"><\/span>C\u00f4ng Ngh\u1ec7 \u00c2m Thanh \u0110i\u1ec1u Ch\u1ec9nh Theo M\u00f4i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y cho ph\u00e9p h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u00e2m thanh t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh theo m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng xung quanh, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e2m thanh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu \u00edch trong c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edf ho\u1eb7c n\u01a1i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16078\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-2.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-2.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-2-600x400.webp 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Cong-nghe-am-thanh-2-768x512.webp 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong_nghe_am_thanh_ket_noi_khong_day\"><\/span>C\u00f4ng Ngh\u1ec7 \u00c2m Thanh K\u1ebft N\u1ed1i Kh\u00f4ng D\u00e2y<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y, vi\u1ec7c truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i \u00e2m thanh gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb tr\u1edf n\u00ean ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i v\u00e0 linh ho\u1ea1t h\u01a1n. Bluetooth, Wi-Fi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y kh\u00e1c \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang ta k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u00e0 chia s\u1ebb \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c.<\/p>\n<p>M\u1ed7i c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u00e2m thanh tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u \u0111a d\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. T\u1eeb \u00e2m thanh 3D cho \u0111\u1ebfn Hi-Res Audio, t\u1eeb n\u00e9n kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t \u0111\u1ebfn \u00e2m thanh \u0111\u1eafm ch\u00ecm, m\u1ed7i c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u1edf ra m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n tr\u1eddi m\u1edbi cho th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u00e2m thanh.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Trong th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u00e2m thanh hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m nghe nh\u00ecn t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u00e1u c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u00e2m thanh h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang ta t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c v\u00e0 \u00e2m thanh xung quanh. C\u00f4ng&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":16080,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[66],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-16077","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/16077","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-js